text: The 1911–12 NC State Wolfpack men's basketball team represents North Carolina State University during the 1911–12 college men's basketball season. The Head coach was Piggy Hargrove coaching the team in his second season. ==Schedule== ==References== Category:NC State Wolfpack men's basketball seasons NC State NC State Wolf NC State Wolf
